features.text:
Welcome to our the Underground Exhibition. Here you can appreciate: (1) The Philosopher's Dark Web3 Tarot, (2) The Eye Gallery NFTs, and (3) the oldest NFTs about Voxels Lore. If you go further into the gallery, you can also find (4) the Web3 Culture NFTs, and (5) some digitalized physical art NFT, some of them with a deep critical aspect. Feel free to appreciate the art and think about the concepts beyond the works. Click the NFTs to read the title and description, and take your time to think about the art. Click the link to check the work in better definition. 

The Philosopher

Drop on Foundation
# Art History Frames

These are the Art History Frames and their owners. There are only 25 unique Art History Frames, and everyone of them comes together with a 1/1 Art History Head for Metaverse and another 1/1 NFT related to the minted Frame. Every holder has the right to substitute an Art History Frame here for his/her own NFT of choice. So you will see in this exhibition also NFTs curated by Art History Frame holders. As soon as all the 25 NFTs are minted, the entire exhibition will be a collectively curated exhibition, only by great collectors who care about art history. Please, feel free to check the exhibition, click the links, and know more about the works curated into this exhibition.

features.text:
Unique Artwork on KnownOrigin & Foundation
# The Frames 1/1

These are the Frames and Collab Frames, created by The Philosopher (FND/KO) and with amazing KnownOrigin Artists (KO). Each frame is a historical piece of collaboration, and they all express a part of our Web3 Culture, with its insertion in the Metaverse Lore Philosopher has been developing within Voxels Community, since the time he was official Voxels storyteller. Renaissance David, Pepe, the Anti-Eye Resistance, the DOS Family, and the Old Hackers are all put together, to show what are being developed. Please, feel free to check the exhibition, click the links, and know more about the works curated into this exhibition. 

The Philosopher

BURNING IS LOVE

THERE IS NO DESTRUCTION ON THE BLOCKCHAIN.

BURNING IS PRESERVING FOREVER INSIDE THE BURN WALLET.

BURNING IS PROTECTION FROM COMMERCE BY THE FOREVER OWNER.

BURNING IS THE SELFLESS ACT SOMEONE CAN DO WITH ONE'S PROPERTY.

BURNING IS TO WRITE THE HISTORY WITH OUR OWN HANDS.

BURN YOUR WORK AND SEND US, TO ENTER IN THE EXHIBITION.

BE SELFLESS, BE CARING...
BURN!

Editions on KnownOrigin

# The Frames Editions

These are the Frames and Collab Frames, created by The Philosopher with amazing KnownOrigin Artists. Each frame is a NFT divided in editions, most of them already part of some private collection. You can nevertheless click in each one and know the description, which talks about the concept we decided for each work. Please, feel free to check the exhibition in the walls of this internal room, click the links, and know more about the works curated into this exhibition. 

The Philosopher

Unique Artwork on Ethereum Blockchain
# The Conceptual Frames - 1/1

On the right, there are the 7 Conceptual Frames, the first ones created by The Philosopher. Each frame talks about an important philosophical, aesthetic, or social question that make us think about the nature of our values. Please, feel free to check the exhibition, click the works for better resolution, and visit the links to know more about the works curated here. 

The Philosopher

Welcome to The Frames Exhibition. Please, click the NFTs to see the art with better resolution and to read the description. The descriptions allow the art appreciator to enjoy the concept with more knowledge. Here you can find philosophical questions about the nature of art and humanity, storytelling about the lore of our metaverse reality, and a deep expression of symbols of web3 culture. The Burning Ritual is in the terrace!

The Philosopher

Please, feel free to check the exhibition, click the links, and know more about the works curated into this exhibition.

Edition Artwork on Foundation/KnownOrigin
# The Frames - Editions

These are the editions of the Frames created by The Philosopher. These ones were created to express in a dark way the spirit of some holidays or characters that move our crypto world. Please, feel free to check the exhibition, click the works for better resolution, and visit the links to know more about the works curated here. 

The Philosopher

This is my most critical and strong work. It says in a loud manner that our christian values are very different from the values of Jesus Christ, who asked us not to discriminate, and accept everyone with love. Love is the key, and for numerous times it is forgotten in our bags of hypocrisy. We through our true values in the golden trash can of our consumerist lives, which demand an irrational segregation that takes us apart, instead of joining us together. What we have thought by Jesus is that God is in the smallest person, the discriminated one, the one who suffers. Life is difficult, and we have no capacity to judge another person's life. Be kind and loving. This is what God expects from us. This work was submitted to a Christmas Scene contest in Ouro Preto; it did not win but made the city to talk about the subject. Click on the Foundation logo to read more. Behind the chair you can find my bronze sculpture with gold leaves, which is a conceptual work to talk about the nature of contemporary art, as a critical homage to Piero Manzoni on tezos blockchain.

The Philosopher
